		<h2>In the spotlight</h2><span></span>
		<ul class="sidebar_feature spotlight">
			<li class="spotlight">
	<a href="/articles/320018.php" title="How gene therapy saved a little boy's life">
	<div>
	<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/headlines/320/320018/stem-cell-treatment.jpg" border="0" width="50%">
	<div class="headline">How gene therapy saved a little boy's life</div>
	<div class="excerpt">Epidermolysis bullosa gives rise to  painful blisters and chronic wounds. Doctors were sure that one little boy was going to lose his life — but he didn't.</div>
	</div>
	</a>
	</li>
		<li class="spotlight">
	<a href="/articles/320005.php" title="Life hacks: Dealing with postpartum depression">
	<div>
	<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://cdn1.medicalnewstoday.com/content/images/headlines/320/320005/woman-with-postpartum-depression-holding-baby.jpg" border="0" width="50%">
	<div class="headline">Life hacks: Dealing with postpartum depression</div>
	<div class="excerpt">The weeks and months after giving birth can be emotional and stressful. Here are some ways to cope if your baby blues become postpartum depression.</div>
	</div>
	</a>
